#: ../../W/winner.rst:5
msgid "winner"
msgstr "winner"

#: ../../W/winner.rst:7
msgid "n\\. An unexpectedly good situation, program, programmer, or person."
msgstr "名詞。思いがけなく良い状況、プログラム、プログラマー、または人。"

#: ../../W/winner.rst:10
msgid ""
"real winner: Often sarcastic, but also used as high praise (see also the "
"note under :ref:`user`\\). \"He's a real winner — never reports a bug till "
"he can duplicate it and send in an example.\""
msgstr ""
"real winner: しばしば皮肉だが、最高の称賛としても使われる(\\ :ref:`user`\\ の項の注も参照)。「彼はreal "
"winnerだ——再現して実例を送れるようになるまで、バグを決して報告しない」。"
